{"lemma":"بَعُوضاتٌ","slug":"بَعُوضاتٌ","root":"ب.ع.ض","root_slug":"ب-ع-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ع-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2897"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B6%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mosquitoes","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"إِنَّ اللهَ لَا يَسْتَحْيِي أَنْ يَضْرِبَ مَثَلاً مَا بَعُوضَةً فَمَا فَوْقَهَا","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ba.ʕuːdˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2897","headword_ar":"بَعُوضٌ","root":"bED","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Gnats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"musquitoes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baq~a","text_ar":"بَقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which signifies both gnats, or musquitoes, (called in Egypt"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAmuws","text_ar":"نَامُوس"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and also bugs]: n. un. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEuwDapN","text_ar":"بَعُوضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baq~apN","text_ar":"بَقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, K.) A poet speaks of the humming of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bEwD","text_ar":"بعوض"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the water. (TA.) The author of the K says, in the B, that the word is taken from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoDN","text_ar":"بَعْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", because of the smallness of the body of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bEwDp","text_ar":"بعوضة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in comparison with other living things. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kal~afaniY mux~a AlbaEuwDi","text_ar":"كَلَّفَنِى مُخَّ البَعُوضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He imposed upon me a difficult thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an impossible thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TS, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","A"]}]}}